long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Sellysium is a marketplace where crafters, makers and designers can browse and buy high quality supplies, tools and accessories from European manufacturers.

Browse a vast inventory of quality European crafting supplies. Be it paper, fabrics, beads, wood, glue or anything else, you will find it here.

To craft wonderful handmade products you will not only need materials, but professional tools of trade as well. No problem, we cover that as well.

Buying the desired goods should not be a thing to worry about. Our trusted, well-known partner makes sure that your payments are safe with us.
